Craddock 200 Cortical Parcellation

Source: R/data.R
craddock200_cortical.Rd

Cortical regions from the Craddock 200-parcel spatially constrained spectral clustering parcellation (Craddock et al., 2012). Contains 2D polygon geometry for ggseg::geom_brain() and 3D vertex indices for ggseg3d::ggseg3d().

Usage

craddock200_cortical()

Value

A ggseg.formats::ggseg_atlas object (cortical).

References

Craddock RC et al. (2012). A whole brain fMRI atlas generated via spatially constrained spectral clustering. doi:10.1002/hbm.21333

See also

Other ggseg_atlases: craddock200_subcortical()

craddock200_cortical()
